# 🐟 About

BigFish-NX is an all-in-one Nintendo Switch CFW package built for users who want a modern, lightweight and easy-to-maintain setup.

Every release is carefully organized, tested and optimized to provide a clean experience.

---

# ✨ Features

✔ Latest Atmosphère

✔ Latest Hekate

✔ Latest Signature Patches

✔ Curated Homebrew

✔ Clean SD Card Layout

✔ Beautiful Boot Logos

✔ Simple Updating

✔ Beginner Friendly

